cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper is about evaluating the performance of visual tracking algorithms, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the importance of model update strategies and image-wide re-detection, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The evaluation methodology and dataset selection are also relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
